# Using Anvil default accounts for local development.
# DO NOT use these keys on any real network.
#
# Start Anvil forking Sepolia:
#   anvil --fork-url $SEPOLIA_RPC_URL
#
# Then:  cp .env.example .env  and set SEPOLIA_RPC_URL to your RPC endpoint.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Sepolia RPC URL (REQUIRED) -------------------------------------------
# Provide your own Sepolia RPC endpoint (Alchemy, Infura, Tenderly, etc.)
